title: Crew Show!
description: This week we sit down to discuss important things like Matt's need to buy unnecessary cars, the King of Hammers, cheeky british saloons with 550HP (Jaguar XFR-S) aftermarket seats, and LA's worst/best strip club/burlesque show Jumbo's Clown Room.  Strap in, take a sip and lean back it's another week of ridiculous crap.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
